#: ../../appendix-01-faq.md:1 0e4e5ca0489a49e89e67f909a274fb18
msgid "Appendix A — Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../appendix-01-faq.md:5 647c9f4d75634fcfb7f8607d7ab9bab6
msgid "General"
msgstr ""

#: ../../appendix-01-faq.md:7 4183cd5d4ed74875b00679e8519d7e0d
msgid "Q: What is Lazy Todo App?"
msgstr ""

#: ../../appendix-01-faq.md:9 0e14e7d3c112412292446e59f30e42d9
msgid ""
"A desktop to-do / task management application built with **Tauri 2 + "
"React + TypeScript**. It runs natively on macOS, Windows, and Linux with "
"a small footprint and offline-first SQLite storage."
msgstr ""

#: ../../appendix-01-faq.md:11 a8e9124b6b5c4961a2531ad7a05b58a6
msgid "Q: Why \"Lazy\"?"
msgstr ""

#: ../../appendix-01-faq.md:13 8e29ba26f6fb48b595f468436cf98f53
msgid ""
"The app is designed to reduce friction — quick capture, minimal clicks, "
"smart defaults. The goal is to let you manage tasks *lazily* "
"(effortlessly), not to encourage laziness."
msgstr ""

#: ../../appendix-01-faq.md:15 5f1ef0527a734efca9ceb56c03b2e6ac
msgid "Q: Is it free / open-source?"
msgstr ""

#: ../../appendix-01-faq.md:17 6e27cd1d11b246b98503c90014853555
msgid ""
"Yes. The project is hosted on GitHub under an open-source license. See "
"the repository root for the exact license file."
msgstr ""

