#: ../../appendix-01-faq.md:54 a3e6cc42e7894317b1f30375512b8ee2
msgid "Q: Rust compilation is very slow on the first build"
msgstr ""

#: ../../appendix-01-faq.md:56 db3fa69990e24f478c4d4957b71492e9
msgid ""
"This is expected. The first `cargo build` downloads and compiles all "
"crate dependencies. Subsequent builds use the cache and are much faster. "
"You can also use `sccache` to speed up repeated clean builds."
msgstr ""

#: ../../appendix-01-faq.md:60 f7405391695446ffbbdb741a1884e982
