msgstr ""

#: ../../appendix-01-faq.md:64 79b8b7f655c34ddab2248215f761718f
msgid ""
"**pnpm** is the project standard. The lock file (`pnpm-lock.yaml`) is "
"committed to the repo. Do not mix with `npm` or `yarn` to avoid lock file"
" conflicts."
msgstr ""

